summary: An ordinance appropriating money from the general fund to reimburse Catherine S. D. Fortman, owner of lots 17, 18, 19 and 20, in block 10, of Blackman's Supplemental Woodland Addition to Salmon Bay City, for moving the fences and other improvements now standing in Phinney Avenue, to conform with the official survey of the City of Seattle and authorizing the drawing of a warrant therefor.
